Package: CPD
Type: Package
Title: CRISPR/Cas9 primer designer
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Jianhong Ou
Maintainer: Jianhong Ou <jianhong.ou@duke.edu>
Description: CPD is a R/Bioconductor package for CRISPR/Cas9 primer design. 
             The input is GenomicRanges object. 
             Output will be multiple excel sheet of primers and off targets.
License: GPL (>=2)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: CRISPRseek, GenomicRanges, BSgenome, ChIPpeakAnno, rtracklayer
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr, RUnit,
          BSgenome.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10, 
          TxDb.Mmusculus.UCSC.mm10.knownGene, 
          org.Mm.eg.db
biocViews: SequenceMatching, Visualization
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
